## üéÆ **Performance Settings**

### **High-End Graphics**
- Full resolution textures (2048x2048)
- Maximum shadow quality
- Full post-processing effects
- High particle counts
- Advanced lighting

### **Medium Graphics**
- Medium resolution textures (1024x1024)
- Medium shadow quality
